[
    {
        "text": "Hi, I’m Francis, ",
        "start": 5.411,
        "duration": 1.422
    },
    {
        "text": "the host of this show \"Cooking with Dog.\"",
        "start": 6.833,
        "duration": 2.898
    },
    {
        "text": "First, let’s cut the ingredients.",
        "start": 18.688,
        "duration": 2.866
    },
    {
        "text": "Trim off the top of the boiled bamboo shoot.",
        "start": 21.704,
        "duration": 3.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, slice the outer part into 5mm slices.",
        "start": 29.024,
        "duration": 5.048
    },
    {
        "text": "Cut the slices into strips.",
        "start": 44.799,
        "duration": 3.385
    },
    {
        "text": "The inside of the bamboo shoot has numerous chambers.",
        "start": 53.869,
        "duration": 4.253
    },
    {
        "text": "Detach the slices along the chamber walls.",
        "start": 58.255,
        "duration": 4.402
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, cut them into 5mm strips again.",
        "start": 66.17,
        "duration": 4.257
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, lightly boil the bamboo shoot in a pot of boiling water.",
        "start": 74.096,
        "duration": 5.437
    },
    {
        "text": "This will help to remove the excess water ",
        "start": 79.799,
        "duration": 2.535
    },
    {
        "text": "and absorb the sauce later.  ",
        "start": 82.334,
        "duration": 2.614
    },
    {
        "text": "Remove and strain it with a mesh strainer.",
        "start": 87.736,
        "duration": 4.07
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, cut the bell pepper in half.",
        "start": 95.221,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Remove the seeds and stem end.",
        "start": 99.889,
        "duration": 3.023
    },
    {
        "text": "Cut the pepper into 5mm strips.",
        "start": 106.944,
        "duration": 3.5
    },
    {
        "text": "A bit of red bell pepper will give it some color.",
        "start": 113.046,
        "duration": 4.201
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, cut the slices of beef steak into 7 to 8mm strips.",
        "start": 121.035,
        "duration": 6.356
    },
    {
        "text": "Place the beef onto a plate.",
        "start": 134.812,
        "duration": 2.496
    },
    {
        "text": "And add the sake, soy sauce, ",
        "start": 137.971,
        "duration": 2.642
    },
    {
        "text": "pepper ",
        "start": 143.692,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "and the sesame oil.",
        "start": 147.519,
        "duration": 2.161
    },
    {
        "text": "Toss to coat with the seasonings.",
        "start": 152.714,
        "duration": 2.715
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s make the sauce.",
        "start": 156.982,
        "duration": 1.801
    },
    {
        "text": "Combine the soy sauce, oyster sauce, ",
        "start": 159.284,
        "duration": 2.522
    },
    {
        "text": "sake, ",
        "start": 164.052,
        "duration": 1.869
    },
    {
        "text": "sugar, ",
        "start": 167.589,
        "duration": 2.169
    },
    {
        "text": "grated garlic ",
        "start": 171.593,
        "duration": 2.165
    },
    {
        "text": "and pepper.",
        "start": 175.843,
        "duration": 1.886
    },
    {
        "text": "Stir to combine well.",
        "start": 179.679,
        "duration": 2.254
    },
    {
        "text": "And now, let’s make the chinjao rosu.",
        "start": 183.412,
        "duration": 3.435
    },
    {
        "text": "Heat the vegetable oil in a pan.",
        "start": 187.782,
        "duration": 2.785
    },
    {
        "text": "Stir-fry the bamboo shoot.",
        "start": 194.618,
        "duration": 2.769
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, add the bell pepper.",
        "start": 205.225,
        "duration": 2.899
    },
    {
        "text": "Lightly season with salt.",
        "start": 211.508,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Continue to stir-fry ",
        "start": 218.38,
        "duration": 1.633
    },
    {
        "text": "until the bell pepper is 3 quarters cooked.",
        "start": 220.013,
        "duration": 3.741
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, place the vegetables onto a plate.",
        "start": 226.968,
        "duration": 3.217
    },
    {
        "text": "Reduce the heat to low.",
        "start": 232.319,
        "duration": 2.335
    },
    {
        "text": "And add the sesame oil.",
        "start": 235.02,
        "duration": 2.336
    },
    {
        "text": "Saute the aromatic vegetables, ",
        "start": 239.439,
        "duration": 2.168
    },
    {
        "text": "ginger root and a white part of the long green onion.",
        "start": 241.607,
        "duration": 4.218
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, add the potato or corn starch to the beef.",
        "start": 249.412,
        "duration": 4.299
    },
    {
        "text": "Toss to coat.",
        "start": 256.104,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "When the aroma grows stronger, add the beef.",
        "start": 262.251,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Stir-fry on medium heat.",
        "start": 269.988,
        "duration": 2.668
    },
    {
        "text": "When the beef is almost cooked, ",
        "start": 279.442,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "add the bell pepper and bamboo shoot.",
        "start": 281.802,
        "duration": 3.308
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, gradually pour in the sauce ",
        "start": 288.313,
        "duration": 2.868
    },
    {
        "text": "and continue stir-frying it on high heat.",
        "start": 291.181,
        "duration": 3.735
    },
    {
        "text": "When the sauce is distributed evenly, ",
        "start": 301.67,
        "duration": 2.666
    },
    {
        "text": "it is ready to serve.",
        "start": 304.336,
        "duration": 2.582
    },
    {
        "text": "Place the chinjao rosu onto a plate.",
        "start": 310.206,
        "duration": 3.253
    },
    {
        "text": "Ta-da!",
        "start": 314.043,
        "duration": 1.515
    },
    {
        "text": "In the original recipes in China, pork is often used ",
        "start": 320.511,
        "duration": 4.202
    },
    {
        "text": "but in Japan using beef is more common.",
        "start": 324.713,
        "duration": 3.702
    },
    {
        "text": "The ingredients are easy to find ",
        "start": 328.415,
        "duration": 2.365
    },
    {
        "text": "so you should definitely try it out.",
        "start": 330.78,
        "duration": 2.629
    },
    {
        "text": "If bamboo shoots are not available in your area, ",
        "start": 341.726,
        "duration": 3.63
    },
    {
        "text": "you can increase the amount of bell peppers.  ",
        "start": 345.356,
        "duration": 2.653
    },
    {
        "text": "Good luck in the kitchen!",
        "start": 348.009,
        "duration": 1.865
    }
]